In the afternoon, head to visit Notre-Dame de Paris, the Ile de la Cite, the Eiffel Tower (exterior) and the Champ de Mars, then take a Seine river cruise to view Les Invalides (exterior), the Grand and Petit Palais (exterior), the Place de la Concorde and other sites, spending the whole day touring the attractions in the center of Paris.
